flowchart TD
    A[Before you go:<br/>create repo 'tacan' with<br/>/client /server /shared folders] --> B[At coworking space:<br/>open Fable 5]

    B --> C[Paste E0-02<br/>monorepo scaffold ticket]
    C --> D[Paste E1-01<br/>board generator]
    D --> E[Ask Fable 5 to write + run<br/>a test proving E1-01's<br/>Acceptance Criteria pass]
    E --> F{Test passes?}
    F -- No --> D
    F -- Yes --> G[Paste E1-02 → repeat<br/>test-verify loop]
    G --> H[... continue through E1-10<br/>one ticket at a time]
    H --> I{All E1-10 tests green?}
    I -- Yes --> J[✅ Stop here for session 1<br/>Rules engine is correct & proven]
    I -- No --> H

    J --> K[Session 2: Epic 2<br/>Colyseus networking<br/>same one-ticket-at-a-time loop]

    style J fill:#1a3a1a,stroke:#66ff66
    style A fill:#1a1a3a,stroke:#6666ff
